verbose_text: The majority of HHT cases are HHT type 1 (HHT1; online mendelian inheritance in man [OMIM] : # 187300) or type 2 (HHT2; OMIM : # 600376), caused by mutations in the endoglin (ENG) or activin receptor like kinase-1 (ACVRL1) genes, respectively [XREF_BIBR].
